imdb.plot outline: "Islanders" let's you relive the 18th Sziget Festival. We look back on the programs of the 5-day non-stop party that is Central-Eastern Europe's biggest music festival. Our hosts Vivi and Dani check out the most exciting cultural, culinary and sporting events happening at Sziget Festival. The two part series includes excerpts from the most mind-blowing concerts of the festival, and exclusive interviews with the top performers including Kaiser Chiefs (UK), Rise Against (USA), Gogol Bordello (USA), and Deftones (USA). We also talk to festival goers from all over the world and showcase the most popular fashion trends of the island festival.
